# group: MIRAgrantReviews
# key: pMIRAnarrowScope
# name: Comment on narrow scope. 
# contributor: Blaine Mooers bmooers1@gmail.com
# --
The RFA for MIRA grant application requires a vision of wide scope.
The current application has a narrow foucs appropriate for a R01 application and lacks the sweeping scope expected for a MIRA.
It is not clear how the proposed research program will advance the field even it is successful in its narrow scope.
